{"tid":261231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"趙國雄：買樓喺親子活動   目前樓市同1997年好唔同","createTime":"2017-05-28T09:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T10:27:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6db0f31b3ddd815d5337138c1baf0d1cb4aebe","tid":261231,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170528/large/1495961006_6379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170528%2Flarge%2F1495961006_6379.jpg&h=81be0f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金管局出招加重8大銀行新造按揭業務資本成本，令多間銀行相繼調高新造拆息（H）按揭息率0.1厘至H＋1.4厘。<br />\n<br />\n長實（1113）執董趙國雄指，「按息仲喺歷史低點，唔會有大影響」，銀行加按息都是「應酬吓」，並形容目前樓市同1997年好唔同，近期入市者以用家為主，而且響可見將來唔會見到息口會大幅增加。<br />\n<br />\n海之戀上周五開售人山人海，趙國雄稱觀察到當日好多父母攜子女到場，相信父母能力許可下都會協助女子置業，更形容「（買樓）喺相當之好嘅親子活動，父母又安心，囝囡更加開心。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記者 陳東陽"},{"pid":"4e363608f95433ddf283f2108aff2c790cf9445d","tid":261231,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02948f4b923d7da9889bf026befc4f9d70fffdd7","tid":261231,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850b7e35ecf016a1b8dd71a2b59296a855cf3525","tid":261231,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"🤣🤣🤣"},{"pid":"0cf1aaa6d44e5bd69c8d327f85d987b8fd62a5a4","tid":261231,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji